ACTRESS Simphiwe Ngema might have gone through a lot these last couple of months, but she has reason to smile again. The former Muvhango star will on Monday make debut appearance on SABC3’s flagship soapie Isidingo. She wil play the role of Phindile. According to the show’s publicist Catherine Sidiyiyo, the actress isn’t there for a short time. “She is in the story for quite some time, so viewers will get enjoy her for a while and the character is an interesting one, but to find out more, viewers will have to tune in and see for themselves,” she said.  She said they are excited to have such a beautiful and talented actress join their cast and “we look forward to forging a relationship with her”.